  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age or older

          -  Estrogen receptor positive (&gt; 1% estrogen expression) by immunohistochemistry

          -  Invasive breast cancer (stage I, II, III) or DCIS considered for adjuvant endocrine
             therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with metastatic disease (stage IV)

          -  Patients less than 18 years of age

          -  Prisoners

          -  Patients are unable to fill prescriptions at the BCC pharmacy due to insurance
             limitations or personal preference
      </textblock>
